VaMBridgeCamera and VaMBridgePerson (Virt‑a‑Mate Bridge Plugins)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

These projects include original code authored by MaryJaneVaM.

They provide lightweight TCP communication utilities and JSON‑based protocol handling
for external control of Virt‑a‑Mate WindowCamera and Person atoms.

Third‑party components used in these projects include:

- UnityEngine (Unity 2018 runtime components)
- Virt‑a‑Mate core assemblies (Assembly‑CSharp, plugin interfaces)
- SimpleJSON (lightweight JSON parsing library)
- .NET / Mono standard library components (System, System.Net.Sockets, etc.)

These components are licensed under their respective open‑source or proprietary licenses.
No modifications have been made to these third‑party libraries, and their licenses and
copyright notices remain the property of their respective authors.

